   "en": "Ikigami no Hanayome"
  },
  "altTitles": [
   {
    "ja": "忌み神の花嫁"
   }
  ],
  "description": {
   "en": "\"I want you to be my bride.\" The company went bankrupt, and the apartment where she lived had a fire... Rin Kamimori suffered a series of disasters. It's the second time she's lost everything, and as if she heard Rin's cry in her heart, \"Somebody help me,\" she lost 20 years ago. Toya) reunite. After being confessed, Rin follows him and is enveloped in a mysterious fog. When she realizes, she is the head of the Kamimori family and that Rin was treated coldly in the past... She was about to perform a ceremony to replace the shrine maiden who receives divine oracles there. So Rin becomes a shrine maiden candidate, but... Set in the present age, the marriage tale of abominable gods and humans begins!",
   "ja": "「俺の花嫁になって欲しい」会社の倒産、住んでいたアパートの火事…立て続けの災難に遭った神守凛(かみもりりん)。なにもかも失うのは2度目、凛の「だれか助けて」という心の叫びを聞いたかのように、20年前に別れたきりの神守透也(かみもりとおや)と再会をする。告白された凛は彼について行くと不思議な霧に巻かれ気が付けば、かつて凛が冷遇されていた神守本家であった…。そこではまさに神の託宣を受ける巫女の代替わりの儀式が行われようとしていた。そこで凛も巫女候補になるが…。現代を舞台に忌み神と人間の婚姻譚開幕!"
  },
